Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H222783&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mortal Combat!!\NX Rider Versus X Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara had completed blueprints for GOD's\NRS Device, which can convert any matter into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanbara escaped GOD and tore the blueprints\Ninto nine pieces to entrust to his old colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has stolen one of the pieces,\Nand the X Rider holds four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the four remaining blueprint pieces?\NAnd will the X Rider or King Dark find them first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Chameleon\NFantômas? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received some interesting information...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This job will require the incarnation\Nof that master of disguise, Fantômas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Just await word of\Nmy inevitable success, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}AB Communications Inc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A malfunction, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? I think the elevator's malfunctioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...? Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Andou...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-who in the world are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Andou, chief of AB Communications'\NTokyo Division. In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't have two versions\Nof the same man running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,S-stop! Someone help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on... I am you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, it's Keisuke!\N-Keisuke, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-What have you been up to lately?\N-Yeah, we've hardly heard from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, how about cutting the\Ngas and making some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right!\N-We'll make it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That ballerina you've been looking for, Kikuchi\NAkiko? Seems she's back from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on the news. Her\Nschool's in Setagaya Ward, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember... Maejima Block 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Kikuchi Ballet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!\NTwo, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, two, three, four, four!\NTwo, three, four, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, three--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, someone's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll be back in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pleasure! Do come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! ...That will be\Nall for today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just came to see someone else\Nwho's been waiting for your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really? And who might that be?\N-A young man named Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke? ...I'm afraid I've\Nnever heard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-It doesn't ring a bell?\N-That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-...Are you sure?\N-Th-that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen too much, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Jin Keisuke looking for you? Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD are bound to have seen the news too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak! Why would Jin Keisuke want to see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! I've told you I don't\Nknow! S-somebody help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't feel like talking, eh?\NThen I'll have to make you!\N-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Jin Keisuke...\NWhat an unsightly fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-C'mon, you can do it!\N-Keep Akiko safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Chameleon Fantômas of GOD's\NVillain Army! Interfere and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's monsters don't get any mercy from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get going, chief!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantômas, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You underestimated the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive my bluntness, but that was\Nnot the full extent of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give our next clash your full attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget that the\NX Rider was powered up recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it inscribed on my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur1\bord0\shad0\pos(0,0)\1c&HD7DBCA&\p1}m 5 102 l 281 102 281 260 5 260{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\1c&H3A4636&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\fscy200\fscx102\fs28\pos(276,124)}Touto General Hospital\N{\fs22\fscy160}Surgery   Internal Medicine  \NPaediatrics   X-Ray
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing serious. She just\Nfainted from the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're awake!\N-And who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm Jin Keisuke.\N-I hear you've been looking for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,May I know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You met a researcher named\NLabique in West Germany, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Labique...?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall. He attended my\Nperformance in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Did he give you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me himself that--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... He did buy me a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He enjoyed my dancing\Nso much that he bought me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be it! Could I\Nhave a look at it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right! The incarnation of the\Nfaceless Fantômas, master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this pendant as a trophy of my victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! Pull yourself together, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That darn Fantômas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly live up to your famous namesake,\NChameleon Fantômas! A job well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...Is what I'd LIKE to say, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's not even a scrap of\Na blueprint inside that pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad idea, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He never guessed that I took\Nit from Akiko on our way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that's another\Nblueprint piece for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara tore the blueprints to his\Nmatter-converting RS Device into nine pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One of his colleagues in West Germany hid this piece\Nin a pendant to be transported to Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cheers!\N-Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-They did it!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, chief! You've still got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was no big deal... I couldn't\Nhave pulled it off without Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, the Kikuchi\NBallet's putting on a show tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-I wanna go!\N-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(1800,0)\fs18\i1}The Kikuchi Akiko Ballet\Npresents Sleeping Beauty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shall we go?\N-I'll be right with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-C'mon!\N-C'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuchi Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Hand over the real blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the ballerina back, bring\Nthe blueprint piece to Hell Valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the blueprint. Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until she's free!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, an exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Release her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry back. Your fans are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, don't tell me you really--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're gonna give it right\Nback, Chameleon Fantômas! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no further use for you now! Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool the X Rider the same way twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm the X Rider!\N-I'm the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bring it on!\N-Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Vacuum Hell Wheel reduces the enemy's offensive power by rolling them along at high speed, driving their head into the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, they're thrown into the\Nair and finished with an X Kick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider defeated Chameleon Fantômas in\Nmortal combat and reclaimed the blueprint piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-She looks so pretty!\N-Doesn't she, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:23:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Kikuchi Akiko's sprite-like dance\Nreaffirmed Keisuke's resolve to fight GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But King Dark's already plotting his next move to acquire the RS Device!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
